videos.description: Jacques Patrick goes up the gut to give the Seminoles the lead on their first drive of the game.
videos.headline: Florida State's Patrick punches in TD

videos.description: Jacques Patrick secures a one-handed catch for 35 yards to Louisiana Monroe's 27-yard line.
videos.headline: Florida State's Patrick one hands catch for 35-yard gain

videos.description: Jacques Patrick runs to the outside for a 45-yard gain to put Florida State at Louisiana Monroe's 30-yard line.
videos.headline: Florida State's Patrick gets to the edge of 45-yard run

videos.description: Cam Akers takes the handoff and bullies his way into the end zone for a 4-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Florida State's Akers fights through for TD run

videos.description: Caleb Evans connects with RJ Turner for 6-yard touchdown, Louisiana Monroe's first of the game.
videos.headline: Turner walks into end zone

videos.description: Cam Akers run gets a huge block and gets around the corner for a 24-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Florida State's Akers runs into end zone untouched

videos.description: Jacques Patrick takes the handoff and springs into the end zone for a 2-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Patrick extends Florida State's lead to 25

videos.description: Ryan Green punches in a 1-yard touchdown as the Seminoles continue to dominate Louisiana Monroe, 42-10.
videos.headline: Florida State's Green pounds it into the end zone

videos.description: Marcus Green juggles the ball and makes the catch while falling down for a 33-yard grab.
videos.headline: Louisiana Monroe's Green makes acrobatic catch

videos.description: Playing under interim coach Odell Haggins, Florida State rushes for 305 yards and five touchdowns in a win over Louisiana Monroe.
videos.headline: FSU secures bowl eligibility with win over Louisiana Monroe
